snippet.title: BIG ICE CREAM | Biggest Stick ice making | Watermelon ice | Kiwi ice | Milk ice | Fruit ice Making
snippet.description:
In our childhood, we enjoy those moments with tasting stick ice. We call this ice "Kuchi ice". Today in our village, we made the three most giant colorful stick ice with fruits and milk. We made three types of ice cream. The first one is milk. The second is watermelon. The third one is Kiwi.

Childhood memory comes again! Tasty!

Today we are going to see how to make less oily and perfect puri. Puri is generally made on festive days like Gudhi padwa, dasara etc. Today we will make such that will absorb less oil. Yes, here are a few tips to make crispy and fluffy puri that absorbs minimum oil. I will give you few tips and tricks during the video. Puri is a popular puffed Indian bread. It is prepared form wheat flour and deep fried. It is mostly enjoyed on festival days with different Indian desserts. The puries should be fluffy and soft. You can try this recipe at home and drop a comment for me. Do not forget to like, share and subscribe.

Ingredients:
‚Ä¢ 2 cups Wheat flour
‚Ä¢ Salt to taste
‚Ä¢ Water 
‚Ä¢ Oil for frying

Method:
‚Ä¢ Mix wheat flour and salt well and add a little water at a time to knead stiff dough. 
‚Ä¢ Cover and rest the dough for at least 15-20 minutes. 
‚Ä¢ Knead the dough well once more until it becomes smooth and even. 
‚Ä¢ You can make small dough balls and roll puris from it. 
‚Ä¢ Or divide the dough into 2 parts and make one of them smooth and even. It has to be 
  smooth. 
‚Ä¢ Keep the left over dough always covered. 
‚Ä¢ Roll out a big chapatti from the dough. The chapatti should be even.  
‚Ä¢ Avoid use of oil or dry flour while rolling the puri. 
‚Ä¢ Make puris with the help of a katori or a lid. 
‚Ä¢ Heat up oil on medium heat. 
‚Ä¢ While dropping puri in hot oil make sure the smooth side should face downwards and the 
  rolled side should be upper side.
‚Ä¢ Drop puri in hot oil and fry well on medium to high heat. 
‚Ä¢ Press a little and when lower side is fried well flip the puri over and fry well from other side 
  too. 
‚Ä¢ When puri is fried well from other side too, take it out, drain excess oil and transfer it into 
  dish. Puri is all ready.
Tips:
‚Ä¢ Avoid use of water while kneading the dough. Do not use hot or cold water when you knead 
  dough. 
‚Ä¢ Always knead stiff dough. 
‚Ä¢ Never make puris immediately after kneading dough. Rest the dough for at least 15-20 
  minutes. 
‚Ä¢ Avoid use of oil or dry flour while rolling the puri. 
‚Ä¢ Make sure you fry each side of puri once. Avoid flipping puri many times.

snippet.title: Iddat | A Short Film | Muskan Sharma | Parinda Films
snippet.description:
"Iddat" is a movie about a girl who elopes and marries a boy from a different caste. Her husband's actions lead to her life being shattered. Will her family forgive her and accept her back into their lives? The movie explores themes of love, forgiveness, and acceptance in the face of difficult circumstances.

snippet.description:
Shekhar Jaiswal Presents Navratri Special Bhajan "Mere Ghar Aao Maiya Navratro Mein"

Edited By - Shekhar Jaiswal

Vlog Channel - https://youtube.com/c/ShekharJaiswalComedy

Booking - 9719998366, 7451940400
Shekharredifmail@gmail.com


Lyrics -
-----------------------------------------

Me to tujhko manau bato bato me..x2
Mere ghar aao maiya navratro me
Mere aao maiya navratro me

Swarg sa laage mohe dwar tumara
Mamta si murat roop hai pyara

Swarg sa laage tera dwara
Mamta ki murat roop hai pyara
Gunj rha sare jag me jaikara
Bada hi sundar laage nazara hoo

Meri dor to maiya tere hatho me..x2
Mere ghar aao maiya navratro me..

Uncha hai parvat lamba hai rasta
Aya shrn jobhi gaya wo hasta

Uncha hai parvat lamba hai rasta
Aya shran jobhi gaya wo hasta
Karti hai kripa maa sherowali
Bichda bhi tere dwar pe milta hoo..
Meri maa mujhko rkhe sar ankhon me..x2
Mere ghar aao maiya navratro me
Mere ghr aao maiya navratro me..

Mom is a noun. It is a shortened form of mother, which means a female parent or matriarch. mother is more likely to appear. A mother's role is to love her children with all her heart. It is also the role of every mom to understand her children. When a child feels this, he or she learns to trust the parents better. ENGLISH GRAMMAR-THE SMART BOOK
A Next Generation Product ( Book + Teachers + Doubt resolution  + Practice + Progress Tracking ) all in one product
Specially Designed for SSC( CGL,CPO,CHSL,STENO) Aspirants

Product Description: This is not an ordinary book. This book is combined with the technology to reduce students' exam preparation time. 
Features:

‚úîÔ∏èEvery Chapter is divided into lectures to give you the feel of class room preparation 

‚úîÔ∏èEvery lecture is a combination of concepts and rules with the questions asked in SSC exams

‚úîÔ∏è Comprehensive coverage of English Grammar as per exam.

‚úîÔ∏èEvery Lecture is taught by awesome Teachers coupled with the technology which is a tab away from you. 

‚úîÔ∏èLast 20 Year PYQs are combined with additional practice questions to cover the 100% content 

‚úîÔ∏èNumerous quizzes are coupled with the help of technology 

‚úîÔ∏èClear instructions for one time read and multiple times read topics

‚úîÔ∏èSummarized the whole book in 100 small bites to set the timetable to complete the course. 

‚úîÔ∏è Doubt resolution tab is combined with the help of technology to resolve your doubt.

‚úîÔ∏è A complete solution ( An alternative of coaching )

‚úîÔ∏è A combination of Book + Teachers + Doubt resolution  + Practice + Progress Tracking 

 Ships in 3 to 4 days after placing the order  
Frequently Asked Questions:
1-Is it a Complete Solution for English Grammar?

Ans- Yes, it is a complete solution. This book is prepared by toppers who are working in the different departments selected through SSC exams. I.e. Shashank - Excise Inspector, JP Sakia: Customs Inspector, Aman-Income tax and many more who have helped to prepare this book. Our Goal is to shorten the time period of preparation.  

2- What is new in this Book which other books are not offering?

This book is prepared with the help of technology. This Book is prepared on a special formula (called content formula)we toppers believe if students prepare through this format they can easily crack the exam. Searching the right contents through various resources is one of the tedious jobs for aspirants. Now you can get all the relevant things like best and rightful contents + best teachers+  Test Analysis + Progress tracking all in one place in the form of digestible unit.  

3- Why is it so special ?

This book is an advance version and first of its kind. It is 10X affordable which will give you  5X speed to prepare your exam.

4- Are toppers recommending this book?

MyPathshala, [1/12/2022 3:03 PM]
Yes, Toppers are not only recommending this book but also promoting this book, because this book can change everything in the life of student. Listen to these toppers
5-How this Book will resolve our doubt ?
During the preparation every student faces this problem. we decided we would build a feature and focus on this part. So we have built the technology and combined it with this book to solve the doubt.  
there is a three layer doubt resolution tab: 
1- we have solved all the questions which are present in this book which are accessible to you with a touch of a button. 
2- we have created a group (not like facebook and telegram) which is controlled by us to solve your doubt. This group will enable you to ask doubt and connect with other aspirants who are preparing for ssc exams. Toppers are accessible in this group to guide you throughout your preparation. 
3- A special provision to ask doubt directly from the teachers.
6- What is the response time of doubt resolution tab?
within -30min if question is asked in working hours

Iss ghar ko chalati hai choti bahu, Kokilaben jissey darte hain saare sadasya. Kokilaben ke bade bete, Ahem ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi se joh hai ek saaf dil ki siddhi saadhi, anpapdh ladki. Unke jethani ke bete, Jigar ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi ki behen, Raashi se joh hai bohot hi chaalaak aur nakhrel. 
              Raashi hamesha dikhati hai neecha Gopi ko aur karti hai uske liye mushkilen taiyaar. Par Gopi ka haath thama Kokilaben ne aur banaya ussey hoshiyaar. Iss saas-bahu ki jodi ne apne pyaar, dulaar aur balidaan se bandhe rakha hai Modi parivaar ko.

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 3724 - Asit Bhai & Tapu Sena Have A Special Announcement! | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3723 - 20 Mar 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3723: Program Ka Chief Guest
--------------------------------------------------------
Popatlal and Sodhi arrive at the clubhouse and are surprised to see it decorated so well. They praise Tapu Sena for such a grand and beautiful arrangement. As they are about to take their seats, Tapu Sena stops them and tells them that the particular space has been reserved for the Chief Guest. Upon asking who the Chief Guest is, Tapu Sena asks them to wait and watch. Later, everybody in the society arrives at the clubhouse one by one and applauds Tapu Sena for their arrangement. But, Tapu Sena does not reveal who their Chief Guest is? Stay tuned to find out!

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3723, 20 Mar 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Namaskar Dosto, aaj ki video mein hum baat karenge Realme C55 ke baare mein jo ki around 10K INR ke Budget price mein aata hai.  Is mein hai MediaTek G88 Processor. Baat karein ager iske Display ki to ye aata hai 6.6 inches FHD+ LCD with 90 Hz Refresh Rate ke saath. Iss phone mein humein milta hai Dual Camera Setup jahan humare pass hai 50 MP Primary Camera, 2MP Mono Camera aur 8MP Front camera. Aur baaki information ke liye poori video dekhein aur like, share, comment karke bataye ki aapko kaisa laga ye realme ka phone. Aage aane vali videos ke liye subscribe karna na bhoolein. 

#RealmeC55 #BudgetSmartphone #TechnicalGuruji #TGFamily

1. Sony Alpha 7S III camera https://www.sony.co.in/electronics/interchangeable-lens-cameras/ilce-7sm3

snippet.title: Downfall of American Banks | Silicon Valley Bank Crash Explained | Dhruv Rathee
snippet.description:
The collapse of the Silicon Valley Bank is the biggest retail banking failure since 2008 and the second biggest banking failure in America's history, following Washington Mutual's collapse. This SVB Crisis had such an impact that it forced the closure of another bank, New York's Signature Bank. But how did this all happen? What went wrong with Silicon Valley Bank? What are the American regulatory bodies doing to fix this? And most importantly, what is the impact of this crisis on India? Watch this video by Dhruv Rathee to find out!

Presenting the Official Trailer of School, College Ani Life. 
In Cinemas 14th April. 

A look at childhood memories, youth, friendship and the love story of a lifetime. School, College Ani Life is a heartwarming, nostalgic look at one man's love affair and the story of a very special friendship with his mentor who guides him in every phase of his life. snippet.title: Meet Kapil Sharma | Episode 90
snippet.description:
Sandeep Maheshwari is a name among millions who struggled, failed and surged ahead in search of success, happiness and contentment. Just like any middle class guy, he too had a bunch of unclear dreams and a blurred vision of his goals in life. All he had was an undying learning attitude to hold on to. Rowing through ups and downs, it was time that taught him the true meaning of his life.

To know more, log on to www.sandeepmaheshwari.com

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - Promoolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son pushes Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalaal.

Click to watch all the Weekly Reliv episodes: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL6Rtnh6YJK7aq_DUPLxBkU49WEPPcecgS

----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

snippet.title: Meet Your Superpower | Motivational Video 2023
snippet.description:
Sandeep Maheshwari is a name among millions who struggled, failed and surged ahead in search of success, happiness and contentment. Just like any middle class guy, he too had a bunch of unclear dreams and a blurred vision of his goals in life. All he had was an undying learning attitude to hold on to. Rowing through ups and downs, it was time that taught him the true meaning of his life.

To know more, log on to www.sandeepmaheshwari.com
